
+) Hamster has 3 actions, when user enters 3 to choose Hamster, the program print the menu:

Hamster
1. Feed
2. Run the treadmill
3. Make sounds
0. Back

     -) if user feeds the hamster, he loses 1 food unit,
     -) if user enters 2, the program will print out: "Sqeak! I am running the treadmill"
     -) if user enters 3, the program will print out: "Sqeak", which is the sound of the hamster

example:
note: ">" indicates user input

 Your balance: $1000
 Your food: 30
 Choose a pet or action:
 1. Cat
 2. Dog
 3. Hamster
 4. Parrot
 5. Buy more food
 0. Exit
 > 3

 Hamster
 1. Feed
 2. Run the treadmill
 3. Make sounds
 0. Back
 > 2
 Sqeak! I am running the treadmill

 Hamster
 1. Feed
 2. Run the treadmill
 3. Make sounds
 0. Back
 > 1
 Sqeak
 You fed the pet

 Hamster
 1. Feed
 2. Run the treadmill
 3. Make sounds
 0. Back
 > 2
 Sqeak! I am running the treadmill

 Hamster
 1. Feed
 2. Run the treadmill
 3. Make sounds
 0. Back
 > 3
 Sqeak

 Hamster
 1. Feed
 2. Run the treadmill
 3. Make sounds
 0. Back
 > 1
 Sqeak
 You fed the pet

 Hamster
 1. Feed
 2. Run the treadmill
 3. Make sounds
 0. Back
 > 0

 Your balance: $1000
 Your food: 28
 Choose a pet or action:
 1. Cat
 2. Dog
 3. Hamster
 4. Parrot
 5. Buy more food
 0. Exit
